short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An easy-to-use unsplash image downloader, including batch download, custom image quality, rename images and other functions

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a simple yet powerful plugin that enables one-click downloading of high-quality images from the Unsplash website.

👨🏻‍💻 Features
✓ Download images one click
✓ Convenient for renaming images
✓ Convenient for downloading images of different resolutions
✓ Save all images in one click
